title: Teng Bespoke Vegetarian Dining
description: Vegetarian Japanese restaurant located in Sunshine Plaza. Serves maki, tempura, sashimi, tofu, udon, soba and tonkatsu dishes. Also sells set meals, which come with a milk-based pudding dessert (vegans can change it to salad). Sushi may contain mayonnaise, so check before ordering. Last order is 30 minutes before closing time.
